    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简介</h2>欢迎来到 Pizza Hero，这款令人兴奋的新型射击 roguelite 游戏为这一类型增添了美味的变化！在这个游戏中，你将扮演一位勇敢的披萨，必须抵御敌人的入侵，保卫世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/64b60c46c0da9dbf161c7d37ae8103a6.poster.avif?t=1748629950\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/64b60c46c0da9dbf161c7d37ae8103a6.webm?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/64b60c46c0da9dbf161c7d37ae8103a6.mp4?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏中战斗时，你将有机会选择各种不同的配料，这些配料会赋予你特殊能力。例如，选择意大利香肠会给你一颗手榴弹，让你造成溅射伤害。或者，如果你感觉勇敢，可以选择蓝奶酪，在你的披萨周围创造一个刺鼻的防御圈，伤害任何靠近的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/fbeea2875e75f20b31c594d2d6ff32b2.poster.avif?t=1748629950\" width=594 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/fbeea2875e75f20b31c594d2d6ff32b2.webm?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/fbeea2875e75f20b31c594d2d6ff32b2.mp4?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>Pizza Hero 是一款 swarm survivor，这意味着你需要运用所有技能和策略来击败一波又一波无情的敌人。游戏中的关卡和能量提升是随机生成的，因此每次游戏体验都是独一无二的。为了帮助你完成任务，游戏还具有自动旋转功能，让你可以轻松切换目标群体，而无需手动旋转。<br><br>所以，如果你准备好接受挑战，保卫世界免受邪恶力量的侵害，现在就来玩 Pizza Hero 吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/a2ebe284850ab1c6304ae443f361b9d6.poster.avif?t=1748629950\" width=686 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/a2ebe284850ab1c6304ae443f361b9d6.webm?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/a2ebe284850ab1c6304ae443f361b9d6.mp4?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内容概览</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15+ 伤害配料<br></li><li>6+ 被动配料<br></li><li>可升级的整体统计<br></li><li>自动旋转/射击控制（可选择集中不同类型的敌人 - 坦克，伤害和支援）<br></li><li>无尽的游戏玩法<br></li><li>生存波次解锁下一个阶段</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/324e6f3d7a977f40a6350c3064c9feac.poster.avif?t=1748629950\" width=610 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/324e6f3d7a977f40a6350c3064c9feac.webm?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202770/extras/324e6f3d7a977f40a6350c3064c9feac.mp4?t=1748629950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告</h2>本游戏包含闪光灯，可能不适合患有光敏性癫痫或其他光敏性疾病的人。建议玩家酌情使用。",
